During Insertion, we insert a node at the and then
compare it with their parents
1. If a parent is smaller than the inserted node then
we swap both of them
2. else inserted node is at the correct position

div.div:
But In heapify we have given a binary tree and
we have to convert it into a Max-Heap.
1. look at the last level each sub-tree is max-heap
2. then look up to the second last level if root are not in max heap
then look upto max weight chid and swap them
3. continue step 2 until the root node
